{"tid":2242974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓外交部：關注bts言論爭議，今後將為發展韓中關係、促進韓中友誼繼續努力","createTime":"2020-10-14T11:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T11:57:30.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8b2490ecc46f9945b25e2d8ee7b53526c61cce88","tid":2242974,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"南韓男子組合「防彈少年團」（BTS）早前涉及韓戰的言論，引起中國網民指責，南韓外交部對事件表示關注。<br />\n<br />\n「防彈少年團」上星期獲頒獎項，以讚揚他們對促進韓美關係有貢獻。成員發表得獎感言時，提及今年是韓戰爆發70周年，會銘記韓美兩國共同經歷的苦難歷史和無數先人的犧牲。有中國網民對此表示強烈不滿，認為「防彈少年團」的發言沒有尊重中方烈士，有辱華之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">南韓外交部表示，為了不影響韓中兩國國民間的相互理解和情感，政府對情況保持關注，今後將為發展韓中關係、促進韓中友誼繼續努力。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，南韓政府南韓兵務廳向國會遞交文件，列明正推進修訂《兵役法》，在文化體育觀光部長官推薦下，容許大眾文化藝術領域優秀藝人，推遲服役及預備役等的徵集日期。兵務廳指，修例目的是通過保障大眾文化藝術活動，提升國家形象，並強調延期服役推薦標準要達致全民共識，在考慮公平性的同時，制定最嚴格的推薦標準。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554566-20201013.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554566-20201013.htm&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2kzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=eeb6c55a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554566-20201013.htm&h=10bb809a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554566-20201013.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b0ba1754a292c336a67a49fd8e2b11e509543715","tid":2242974,"uid":75656,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"BTS同fans各捐一百萬美元支持blm<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2067223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2067223&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2kzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=b3bd1c68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2067223</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=394565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394565&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2kzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=28b352fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394565&h=42b1d7fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=394565</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/hot/player?newsId=395336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395336&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2kzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=fbfa6187\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395336&h=603ad48c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/hot/player?newsId=395336</a><br />\n<br />\nBts同班fans對住trump都未驚過，仲捐埋錢支持blm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好心南韓政府學下野，唔好咁快跪la<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b27713e1ef2b527e310faa3da6eace99b98c2b","tid":2242974,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:49:38.000Z","msg":"左膠寅"},{"pid":"69cb34ae80da1b2bc1163967d8f39eb73c2cec54","tid":2242974,"uid":181789,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"南韓你返去食屎啦"},{"pid":"e4f68033a6ba8a950254495972ee231f165a4ca5","tid":2242974,"uid":310700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:52:50.000Z","msg":"共同民主黨，my韓國"},{"pid":"014a434e8d2ab6d203ebdbef6648603b8beabfa3","tid":2242974,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:53:13.000Z","msg":"共產黨又跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地藍絲日日輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88594279b2644f2d4b083f27b443b3f5b989fe26","tid":2242974,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":